{"tid":402394,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"20:15【安娜貝爾2：誕生 Annabelle: Creation 2017】","createTime":"2017-09-16T11:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T14:03:44.000Z","uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c935d6b77584a351ecb280de7f1adddeae7727f","tid":402394,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=Xlf0lsyH9VACQRQFIBnRs8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c220edf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　由約翰&middot;R&middot;萊昂耐迪執導，安娜貝拉&middot;沃麗絲、阿爾法&middot;沃德主演的低成本恐怖片《安娜貝爾》，去年在美國上映後反響不錯。如今有消息稱，新線電影公司打算開拍續集，劇本仍由原片編劇Gary Dauberman撰寫，將延續原作的風格和特色。 <br />\n　　《安娜貝爾》是溫子仁恐怖系列《招魂》的外傳電影，在恐怖元素的基礎上，增加了更多暴力和血腥的內容。影片的故事講述了一對新婚夫婦的恐怖經歷，在妻子懷孕後，丈夫帶回了妻子尋覓已久的娃娃安娜貝爾，從此接二連三的厄運也朝著這對夫婦襲來&hellip;&hellip;作為一部衍生電影，如今能獲拍續集發展為系列片，可見其故事大有發展空間。 <br />\n　　目前，《安娜貝爾》續集只確定了編劇的回歸，原片導演、主演等主創暫無回歸的消息傳出<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.popnews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Screen-Shot-2017-07-28-at-1.34.45-PM-600x488.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.popnews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FScreen-Shot-2017-07-28-at-1.34.45-PM-600x488.png&h=25f0d9d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87473ee4c68d913f1a75b8daa1d16a2e999c025a","tid":402394,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"2ad0e6a3683e00a753cac10f3d7c0bad8504d0e8","tid":402394,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"299daea6bced2916e43b01a392cff13c4845a390","tid":402394,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"c3f8a34516e5246ccbcb9780